-- `skill-plans.ts`: deterministic action derivation from status for each supported skill.
-- `executor.ts`: shared policy checks, dispatch audit planning, consent reuse, blocked action handling.
-- `index.ts`: MCP entrypoints only, no orchestration logic beyond dependency wiring.
-- `status.ts`: stays read-oriented, but can expose small helpers the runner needs for terminal-state checks if required.
